source.name: Movie Names
source.description: If you love movies, and you love San Francisco, you're bound to love this -- a listing of filming locations of movies shot in San Francisco from 1924 - 2010. You'll find the titles, locations, fun facts, names of the director, writer, actors, and studio for most of these films.
